item.title: Cyrus "Glitch" Spencer & Sarah (aka Phoenix lil'Mini) Animation Freestyle - Dancersglobal.tv
item.description:
Cyrus "Glitch" Spencer & Sarah (aka Phoenix lil'Mini) Animation Freestyle - Dancersglobal.tv

Cyrus "Glitch" Spencer was in Sacramento, CA as part of the Excel In Motion Dance Convention tour, and during that time we were able to film several videos. This particular video, however, was very special. 8-year-old Sarah (aka Phoenix lil'Mini) was given the awesome opportunity to film this dance video with "Glitch" after only meeting him a few hours prior to filming!
